  '<li><strong>DGA entropy heuristic</strong> — high-entropy single labels (Shannon entropy ≥ 3.8 bits/char on labels ≥ 12 chars) are C2 / DGA shape (Mirai / Conficker family). Heuristic-not-rule — operators tune <code>dgaEntropyThreshold</code> + <code>dgaMinLabelLen</code>.</li>',
